support.descp:
You will get a PDF copy of Noctis Labyrinth, plus any digital stretch goals we're able to unlock:
* Fire-Eye ruins map;
* Full color PDF alternative version;
* Cardea, City of Dominion;
*Tharsis, the City of Liquid Fire.

You will get a black and white physical version of Noctis Labyrinth, plus any digital stretch goals we're able to unlock:
* Fire-Eye ruins map;
* Full color PDF alternative version;
* Cardea, City of Dominion;
*Tharsis, the City of Liquid Fire.
~ UNLESS ~ we unlock the colored paper stretch goal, in which case your physical copy of Noctis Labyrith will be over colored paper, with each chapter color coded for your enjoyment.
Domestic US shipping is covered. International shippings will have to be paid separately.
